third-party components above is done under the following premises:

  - Each component is redistributed unmodified.
  - End users of the resulting Propr stack bring their own credentials
    and accept the upstream providers' terms of service directly.
  - No repackaging, rebranding, or circumvention of upstream billing or
    authentication occurs.

If you are an upstream maintainer who wishes to object to or clarify the
